            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4 mb-5">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm text-center">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="card-icon mb-3"><i class="fas fa-print fa-2x"></i></div>
                    <h5 class="card-title">Digital & Printing</h5>
                    <p class="card-text small text-muted">High-quality printing, binding, lamination, business cards, and more for all your personal and professional needs.</p>
                    <a href="/services#digital-printing" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm text-center">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="card-icon mb-3"><i class="fas fa-laptop-code fa-2x"></i></div>
                    <h5 class="card-title">Computer Education</h5>
                    <p class="card-text small text-muted">Empowering you with essential computer skills through our comprehensive training programs. From basics to MS Office proficiency.</p>
                     <a href="/services#computer-education" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">View Courses</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm text-center">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="card-icon mb-3"><i class="fas fa-landmark fa-2x"></i></div>
                    <h5 class="card-title">Government Services</h5>
                    <p class="card-text small text-muted">Expert assistance with eCitizen applications, KRA services, NHIF registration, and other essential government paperwork.</p>
                    <a href="/services#government-services" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary">Learn More</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="row align-items-md-stretch gx-4 gy-4">
