                <p>Access your course materials, view academic scores, check fee statements, and stay updated with important announcements. Login to get started with your learning journey.</p>
                <a href="/student/login" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg" type="button">Go to Student Portal</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="h-100 p-5 bg-light border rounded-3 shadow">
                <h2><i class="fas fa-user-shield me-2"></i>Admin Area</h2>
